description: Returns contact list metadata. It does not return any information about the contacts present in the list.

parameters.name: ContactListName
parameters.description: The name of the contact list.

nested_items.name: ContactListName
nested_items.description: The name of the contact list.

nested_items.name: Topics
nested_items.description: An interest group, theme, or label within a list. A contact list can have multiple topics.

nested_items.name: DisplayName
nested_items.description: The name of the topic the contact will see.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: A description of what the topic is about, which the contact will see.

nested_items.name: DefaultSubscriptionStatus
nested_items.description: The default subscription status to be applied to a contact if the contact has not noted their preference for subscribing to a topic.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: A description of what the contact list is about.

nested_items.name: CreatedTimestamp
nested_items.description: A timestamp noting when the contact list was created.

nested_items.name: LastUpdatedTimestamp
nested_items.description: A timestamp noting the last time the contact list was updated.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: The tags associated with a contact list.
